{"tid":1438602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家唔好搞鳩國泰","createTime":"2019-08-09T21:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T09:08:51.000Z","uid":76751,"like":90,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8aca2b3a6dd039e1a63e1c0c9c11323d6b24c1","tid":1438602,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:19:58.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完個post:<br />\n<br />\n由即日起，國泰或其他嘅香港空中機組人員罷飛中國大陸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438350</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n其實罷飛最大損失係國泰，我唔太明罷飛對政權或者中共有乜影響，真正要罷工既係機場(機管局同控制塔)先可以影響到政府<br />\n<br />\n成件事國泰係比人揸住春袋同做左磨心，佢航線要經大陸冇得選擇，中共明顯係玩緊國泰，你班連登仔仲要加多腳，中共見你地自己友打自己友不知幾開心<br />\n<br />\n其實搞死國泰根本無好處，反而可能比國航食水，大家唔好再搞鳩國泰，支持下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有錯可以指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727d87f81e9f8ce4ffd367b41c7a8f4246fcde26","tid":1438602,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:21:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b69fefe4ebdbc0778dc2756539f3a36cee9fe5fe","tid":1438602,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:21:32.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c26ad86cac8b6fd0b01f80795c0b550272611a9e","tid":1438602,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:22:11.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"08dc5d484ffeb1dc7293ae09589bdd503747f8f3","tid":1438602,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:22:32.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a22c82613ad4faea6842938f2cb47f836cf2c3f1","tid":1438602,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:22:43.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61889957dc81e11f6654f6eba4b16711e16365f","tid":1438602,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:23:15.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/